  <body>
    <header><para styleclass="Heading1">Example - Performance</para></header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A representative cold-boot transcript: power-up, the Loadable Firmware Update (LFU) utility, an <text styleclass="Code Example">update srm</text>, and the interactive <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> prompt with a few <text styleclass="Code Example">show</text> / <text styleclass="Code Example">set</text> commands. Spacing is simplified for readability.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">ASA EmulatR -- Alpha AXP (EV6 / 21264) Emulator</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Alpha Emulator Console V4.0-0</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">(c) 2026 Timothy Peer / eNVy Systems, Inc.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">*** keyboard not plugged in...</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Flash ROM writes are disabled</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">1024 Meg of system memory</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">probing hose 0, PCI</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">probing PCI-to-ISA bridge, bus 1</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">bus 0, slot 5 -- dqa -- Cypress 82C693 IDE</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">initializing GCT/FRU at 3f32000</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Checking dqa0.0.0.105.0 for the option firmware files. . .</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">dqa0.0.0.105.0 has no media present or is disabled via the RUN/STOP switch</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Checking dva0.0.0.0.0 for the option firmware files. . .</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Option firmware files were not found on CD or floppy.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">... or just hit &lt;return&gt; to proceed with a standard console update:</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">      ***** Loadable Firmware Update Utility *****</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Function   Description</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Display    Displays the system's configuration table.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Exit       Done exit LFU (reset).</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> List       Lists the device, revision, firmware name, and update revision.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Update     Replaces current firmware with loadable data image.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Verify     Compares loadable and hardware images.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt; update srm</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Confirm update on:</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">srm              [Y/(N)]y</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">WARNING: updates may take several minutes to complete for each device.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">             DO NOT ABORT!</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">srm        Updating to 7.3-1...  Verifying 7.3-1...  PASSED.</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt; exit</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> Initializing....</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Testing the System</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Testing the Disks (read only)</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">snapshot Console V7.3-2, Feb 27 2007 13:25:53</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Halt Button is IN, AUTO_ACTION ignored</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;show config</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">SRM Console:    V7.3-2</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">PALcode:        OpenVMS PALcode V1.98-83, Tru64 UNIX PALcode V1.92-73</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Processors</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">CPU 0           Alpha EV6 pass 1 268 MHz</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">                SROM Revision:  P&lt;?&gt;</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">                Bcache is disabled</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Core Logic</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Cchip       DECchip 21272-CA Rev 2</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Dchip       DECchip 21272-DA Rev 1</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Pchip 0     DECchip 21272-EA Rev 1</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">TIG         Rev 7.31</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Arbiter     Rev 7.31 (0xff)</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">MEMORY</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Array #     Size       Base Addr</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">   0        1024 MB    000000000</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Total Good Memory = 1024 MBytes</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">PCI Hose 00</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">    Bus 00  Slot 05/0: Cypress 82C693</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">                       Bridge to Bus 1, ISA</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">    Bus 00  Slot 05/1: Cypress 82C693 IDE</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">                       dqa0.0.0.105.0   EMULATR VIRTUAL CDROM</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">ISA  (Slot/Device/Name/Type/Enabled/BaseAddr/IRQ/DMA)</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  0  MOUSE   Embedded  Yes  60   12</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  1  KBD     Embedded  Yes  60   1</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  2  COM1    Embedded  Yes  3f8  4</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  3  COM2    Embedded  Yes  2f8  3</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  4  LPT1    Embedded  Yes  3bc  7</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">  5  FLOPPY  Embedded  Yes  3f0  6   2</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;show device</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">dqa0.0.0.105.0          DQA0     EMULATR VIRTUAL CDROM</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">dva0.0.0.0.0            DVA0</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;show memory_test</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">memory_test         full</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;set memory_test none</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;set full_powerup_diags off</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;show memory_test</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">memory_test         none</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</para>
